hopobject.body: A pension scheme indianamedicaid.com Lady Gaga has never been one who's big on wearing actual clothing, so it only seems normal that the star would find this completely see-through outfit appropriate for traveling. Gaga donned the sheer black ensemble while arriving at Vnukovo aiport in Moscow, where she gave fans a good look at her black bra from every angle. She accessorized the getup with fishnet stockings and sky-high heels -- typical Gaga attire.
